om/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2Fr8kxar.html&d=RkDpb%2Fugp%2FKDARkKXTmhTtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=840d691e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/entertainment/r8kxar.html</a>"},{"pid":"66a7293c842f7d7425fb7d47acf94eec199ba969","tid":425934,"uid":22643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"星爺d戲女主有多d發揮得幾個<br />\n梅姐 靚靚 朱恩 張敏（只限九品 做得真係幾好）"},{"pid":"04e5b70801813cf017e8e76850ceee5b7e9c90a1","tid":425934,"uid":20924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"有波無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee989b4f5483def5e79689d0809427bd37657221","tid":425934,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星爺d戲女主有多d發揮得幾個<br />\n梅姐 靚靚 朱恩 張敏（只限九品 做得真係幾好）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n栢芝 林青霞 火雞姐"},{"pid":"b1b614809447b161ff50efe068585bb9730df0bf","tid":425934,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>星爺d戲女主有多d發揮得幾個<br />\n梅姐 靚靚 朱恩 張敏（只限九品 做得真係幾好）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n栢芝 林青霞 火雞姐</blockquote><br />\n早兩日先睇番西遊記 藍潔瑛都唔錯"},{"pid":"718a1c88d1dc4c7012b1acbcfb3ea6ffc1485229","tid":425934,"uid":13257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:54:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/-VT8X3L2IHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-VT8X3L2IHw&d=RkDpb%2Fugp%2FKDARkKXTmhTtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8c34617d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-VT8X3L2IHw</a><br />\n<br />\n咁睇拱脷啲戲好好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解會有呢個版本架？</blockquote><br />\n在香港電影中，王晶導演周潤發主演的《賭神》取得成功後，引起一片賭片跟風，劉鎮偉找到周星馳拍了《賭聖》，加入特異功能元素使得影片大賣，而周星馳也一舉成名。拍電影以「賺錢為目的」王晶便趁機拉來周星馳拍了這部《賭俠2上海灘賭聖》。在當時的香港，電影主要市場為台灣。而台灣當時尚在實行「電影中不准有大際明星參演」的政